Avatars,io,is,an,avatar,hosting,service,It,is,designed,for,integration,with,mobile,apps,and,websites,Developers,can,use,the,Avatars,io,to,host,the,avatars,their,users,assign,themselves,After,they,are,uploaded,the,avatars,can,be,retrieved,at,different,sizes,Avatars,io,is,fully,compatible,with,Gravatars,and,social,media,sites,like,Twitter,Instagram,and,Facebook,The,entirety,of,Avatars,io,functionality,is,a,RESTful,API,that,exposes,avatar,upload,and,retrieval,It,returns,JSON,formatted,data